, Peninsula Esmeralda &amp; Laguna San Rafael) and in adjacent W 
<collectingCountry box="[2125,2267,1495,1528]" name="Argentina" pageId="31" pageNumber="438">Argentina</collectingCountry>
from SW 
<collectingRegion country="Argentina" name="Neuquen" pageId="31" pageNumber="438">Neuquén Province</collectingRegion>
, southward along the foothills of the Andes to Los Alerces National Park in 
<collectingRegion box="[2078,2317,1612,1645]" country="Argentina" name="Chubut" pageId="31" pageNumber="438">Chubut Province</collectingRegion>
